                     <interp inst="t17860719-55-person614" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>This is the grate.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>A man hired me to carry it.</p>
